            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">Using mirrors to reflect positive energy.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Placing plants like bamboo or Tulsi to promote vitality and health.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Using crystals or gemstones to balance energy in specific rooms.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Placing symbols like Swastika or Om to bring good fortune and spiritual harmony.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

